description:
A tech demo to showcase the mechanics of the upcoming action game "Survive Custom : Divergent Conflicts"
 
&gt;Objective&lt; 
<p> The task is to find the exit out of the facility node.</p>

&gt;Gameplay&lt; 
<p>This is a short demo which lasts for a few minutes of game-play depending on your skill. You will be expected to discover the controls yourself as there will be no tutorial.</p>
<p>Work your way through it and after that, hunt for the secret Gold-Box easter egg.</p>

